Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.69,0:00:18.57,OP-ED,NTP,0,0,0,,黑暗之中 震撼心灵
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.57,0:00:21.74,OP-ED,NTP,0,0,0,,那觉醒的开始
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.99,0:00:24.78,OP-ED,NTP,0,0,0,,立于大地的那身姿
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.87,0:00:27.95,OP-ED,NTP,0,0,0,,是否为正义的证明？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.08,0:00:32.04,OP-ED,NTP,0,0,0,,传说巨神的那力量
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.25,0:00:35.00,OP-ED,NTP,0,0,0,,直把银河切裂！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.17,0:00:38.25,OP-ED,NTP,0,0,0,,他战斗时的那吼声
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.25,0:00:41.09,OP-ED,NTP,0,0,0,,招来闪电雷霆！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.09,0:00:44.14,OP-ED,NTP,0,0,0,,不要颤抖啊 紧紧盯着哟
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.22,0:00:49.51,OP-ED,NTP,0,0,0,,那复活的时刻！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.06,0:00:56.27,OP-ED,NTP,0,0,0,,人们还有生灵们 看着这开始的时刻
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.56,0:01:02.19,OP-ED,NTP,0,0,0,,宇宙的逃亡者伊迪安 伊迪安
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.53,0:01:09.20,OP-ED,NTP,0,0,0,,宇宙的逃亡者伊迪安 伊迪安
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.22,0:01:29.80,Default,,0,0,0,,索罗船和达拉姆队的激战中
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.45,0:01:32.11,Default,,0,0,0,,科斯摩与吉杰进行了对决
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.80,0:01:39.22,Default,,0,0,0,,但是 因失血过多而神志不清的科斯摩
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.77,0:01:44.62,Default,,0,0,0,,并不知道女友琪吉·琪珍的死 继续昏睡着
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.65,0:01:51.62,T,,0,0,0,,{\pos(242.144,160.686)}死斗·盖尔的恐怖
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.65,0:01:51.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs22}翻译：Ross.H 校对：Ross.H&H魂  时轴：H魂 后期：Ross.H 繁化：kinson
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.00,0:03:04.68,Default,,0,0,0,,像这样睁不开眼睛 得多久呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.11,0:03:08.37,Default,,0,0,0,,科斯摩是坚强的人  他一定没事的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.14,0:03:19.25,Default,,0,0,0,,发现外星人的船
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.17,0:03:22.54,Default,,0,0,0,,意外的迅速呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.34,0:03:25.31,Default,,0,0,0,,我们这船真不错
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.45,0:03:30.71,Default,,0,0,0,,哈鲁鲁那家伙 明明可以准备性能更优越的船来
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.54,0:03:36.17,Default,,0,0,0,,但这艘船搭载了\N令人神往的新兵器 重机动机甲伽尔波·吉克
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.37,0:03:38.28,Default,,0,0,0,,我已经知足了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.82,0:03:40.74,Default,,0,0,0,,它是为了对抗巨人而开发的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.91,0:03:44.25,Default,,0,0,0,,尽情地发挥取得战果吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.20,0:03:49.34,Default,,0,0,0,,本来我觉得它还需要测试
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.80,0:03:52.77,Default,,0,0,0,,没关系 只要能打倒巨人的话...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.11,0:03:55.45,Default,,0,0,0,,哈鲁鲁也变了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.54,0:03:56.20,Default,,0,0,0,,啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.37,0:04:00.65,Default,,0,0,0,,她给了我们预想以上的战力
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.20,0:04:03.51,Default,,0,0,0,,是为了表现自己的心情吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.54,0:04:06.65,Default,,0,0,0,,作为女人 她也有可爱的一面啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.25,0:04:07.71,Default,,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.02,0:04:12.05,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯？ 科斯摩醒来了？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.62,0:04:36.17,Default,,0,0,0,,琪吉·琪珍死了...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.94,0:04:39.45,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么能让她这样无辜的平民死掉呢...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.54,0:04:42.45,Default,,0,0,0,,琪吉·琪珍？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.80,0:04:45.14,Default,,0,0,0,,是科斯摩在凯拉尔认识的女孩
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.94,0:04:48.57,Default,,0,0,0,,杀戮的事让双方的军人做就可以了...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.37,0:04:50.57,Default,,0,0,0,,你说是不是啊 贝斯
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.48,0:04:52.42,Default,,0,0,0,,是不是啊 谢莉鲁
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.82,0:04:56.37,Default,,0,0,0,,科斯摩...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.97,0:04:57.60,Default,,0,0,0,,可恶！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.48,0:05:00.82,Default,,0,0,0,,你干什么 科斯摩
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.02,0:05:02.11,Default,,0,0,0,,还得卧床休息
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.48,0:05:05.68,Default,,0,0,0,,我能睡得着吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.31,0:05:07.02,Default,,0,0,0,,能睡得着吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.11,0:05:07.65,Default,,0,0,0,,科斯摩
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.97,0:05:08.65,Default,,0,0,0,,睡一会儿吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.88,0:05:10.54,Default,,0,0,0,,罗达 随便他
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.34,0:05:12.02,Default,,0,0,0,,这就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.85,0:05:18.28,Default,,0,0,0,,可恶！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.40,0:05:23.20,Default,,0,0,0,,真不像样 男人哭的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.65,0:05:24.65,Default,,0,0,0,,真不像样
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.62,0:05:28.05,Default,,0,0,0,,你知道些什么啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.62,0:05:29.25,Default,,0,0,0,,你这家伙...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.57,0:05:32.60,Default,,0,0,0,,科斯摩 不要计较
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.57,0:05:35.71,Default,,0,0,0,,我不管什么人情 别说好话
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.02,0:05:38.51,Default,,0,0,0,,说好话？我吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.77,0:05:40.54,Default,,0,0,0,,科斯摩 这样不好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.62,0:05:41.62,Default,,0,0,0,,没事的 罗达
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.02,0:05:42.85,Default,,0,0,0,,谢莉鲁小姐...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.65,0:05:45.14,Default,,0,0,0,,这真不像样啊 科斯摩
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.62,0:05:46.51,Default,,0,0,0,,小鬼不要烦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.77,0:05:49.34,Default,,0,0,0,,科斯摩
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.77,0:05:50.80,Default,,0,0,0,,小鬼闭嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.31,0:05:52.05,Default,,0,0,0,,科斯摩...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.71,0:05:53.65,Default,,0,0,0,,振作啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.34,0:06:02.68,Default,,0,0,0,,不要自作主张...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.74,0:06:08.42,Default,,0,0,0,,科斯摩
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.20,0:06:11.05,Default,,0,0,0,,大家都要依靠你
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.85,0:06:15.20,Default,,0,0,0,,虽然明白你的心情 但除了忍耐没其他的办法啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.51,0:06:16.02,Default,,0,0,0,,科斯摩...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.57,0:06:17.34,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.17,0:06:19.02,Default,,0,0,0,,虽然我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.68,0:06:20.22,Default,,0,0,0,,但是我
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.74,0:06:23.17,Default,,0,0,0,,我连跟琪吉·琪珍说声再见也没来得及啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.31,0:06:23.91,Default,,0,0,0,,可恶！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.57,0:06:27.25,Default,,0,0,0,,可恶...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.08,0:06:36.48,Default,,0,0,0,,科斯摩？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.17,0:06:40.60,Default,,0,0,0,,科斯摩！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.08,0:06:41.57,Default,,0,0,0,,没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.74,0:06:48.22,Default,,0,0,0,,我自己会做点什么 别担心了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.08,0:06:50.02,Default,,0,0,0,,我们去哪里？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.40,0:06:51.02,Default,,0,0,0,,地球
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.65,0:06:52.28,Default,,0,0,0,,地球？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.22,0:06:55.77,Default,,0,0,0,,索罗船的残存兵力是无法打败敌人的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.25,0:06:58.48,Default,,0,0,0,,我们得向宇宙联合军补充战力
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.77,0:07:02.28,Default,,0,0,0,,而且回地球 那里的科技也能分析第六文明人留下的谜团
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.17,0:07:05.00,Default,,0,0,0,,真的甩掉巴夫·克兰了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.57,0:07:06.57,Default,,0,0,0,,正有这个打算
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.25,0:07:10.05,Default,,0,0,0,,而且我们已经知道巴夫·克兰星的位置了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.74,0:07:11.62,Default,,0,0,0,,实在不行的话...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.97,0:07:12.45,Default,,0,0,0,,啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.48,0:07:14.77,Default,,0,0,0,,卡拉拉告诉我们了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.65,0:07:16.25,Default,,0,0,0,,但是...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.05,0:07:18.40,Default,,0,0,0,,如果回地球去
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.31,0:07:21.62,Default,,0,0,0,,我就不能亲手为琪珍报仇了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.71,0:07:23.71,Default,,0,0,0,,因为这种个人理由去战斗...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.31,0:07:29.17,Default,,0,0,0,,有船正在追着索罗船
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.48,0:07:30.97,Default,,0,0,0,,什么 引擎室！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.20,0:07:32.51,Default,,0,0,0,,主引擎出力最大
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.65,0:07:34.71,Default,,0,0,0,,甩掉他们 全员准备
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.20,0:07:35.85,Default,,0,0,0,,是巴夫·克兰？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.48,0:07:37.54,Default,,0,0,0,,还没放弃吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.80,0:07:38.51,Default,,0,0,0,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.00,0:07:40.88,Default,,0,0,0,,我们正要回故乡啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.22,0:07:43.20,Default,,0,0,0,,还得找个行星躲起来吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.85,0:07:46.31,Default,,0,0,0,,必须甩掉他们 专心工作
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.51,0:07:52.65,Default,,0,0,0,,好恶心...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.37,0:07:59.02,Default,,0,0,0,,你这种身体不能出击的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.08,0:08:00.68,Default,,0,0,0,,啊 路 别这样
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.68,0:08:11.11,Default,,0,0,0,,试着停止DS航行吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.65,0:08:15.14,Default,,0,0,0,,我要确认一下是不是巴夫·克兰在追踪我们
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.80,0:08:18.91,Default,,0,0,0,,再这样逃亡下去 还能向地球请求援军吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.40,0:08:20.68,Default,,0,0,0,,要去地球吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.85,0:08:23.08,Default,,0,0,0,,不能把我们自己的星球卷进去
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.60,0:08:24.94,Default,,0,0,0,,战斗完再回地球更好
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.62,0:08:26.60,Default,,0,0,0,,科斯摩说的对
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.28,0:08:28.34,Default,,0,0,0,,停止DS航行！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.68,0:08:33.11,Default,,0,0,0,,消失了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.88,0:08:36.77,Default,,0,0,0,,洛古·丹外星人的船中止亚空间航行了！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.20,0:08:38.57,Default,,0,0,0,,探查他们逃到了哪个空域
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.22,0:08:40.91,Default,,0,0,0,,要出动吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.48,0:08:45.85,Default,,0,0,0,,不要大意 外星人的行动比往常都要快
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.91,0:08:48.62,Default,,0,0,0,,好 那我去驾驶伽尔波·吉克
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.94,0:08:49.25,Default,,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.57,0:08:56.08,Default,,0,0,0,,要表示对哈鲁鲁的感激吗...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.51,0:09:13.05,Default,,0,0,0,,敌人来了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.25,0:09:14.82,Default,,0,0,0,,4点的方位
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.37,0:09:17.28,Default,,0,0,0,,三分钟内进入导弹射程
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.08,0:09:19.37,Default,,0,0,0,,科斯摩 你别勉强了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.25,0:09:22.91,Default,,0,0,0,,我还能看清敌人的攻击 不会输的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.74,0:09:25.54,Default,,0,0,0,,我必须为琪珍报仇
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.05,0:09:28.37,Default,,0,0,0,,就是因为你这种个人的理由
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.48,0:09:29.88,Default,,0,0,0,,能打赢的战斗反而赢不了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.37,0:09:32.20,Default,,0,0,0,,我赢给你看！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.25,0:09:35.40,Default,,0,0,0,,等着我赢给你看吧...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.57,0:09:47.14,Default,,0,0,0,,迪克
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.62,0:09:48.20,Default,,0,0,0,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.00,0:09:51.91,Default,,0,0,0,,那是当然的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.48,0:09:54.57,Default,,0,0,0,,刚才的事对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.20,0:09:58.54,Default,,0,0,0,,我也挺喜欢琪吉·琪珍的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.57,0:10:01.85,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢 你这样说真是太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.68,0:10:11.65,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么了 科斯摩
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.20,0:10:12.74,Default,,0,0,0,,没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.71,0:10:19.17,Default,,0,0,0,,你看不清吗 科斯摩
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.22,0:10:21.17,Default,,0,0,0,,闭嘴 迪克
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.88,0:10:22.42,Default,,0,0,0,,但是...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.88,0:10:24.48,Default,,0,0,0,,被大家知道就糟糕了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.54,0:10:26.80,Default,,0,0,0,,那样就报不了仇了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.88,0:10:29.40,Default,,0,0,0,,行吗 别再说了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.82,0:10:30.25,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.45,0:10:32.85,Default,,0,0,0,,这是男人之间的约定
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.62,0:10:38.20,Default,,0,0,0,,知道了 我会代替你的眼睛的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.11,0:10:42.45,Default,,0,0,0,,但是 只为了琪吉·琪珍一个人战斗是不行的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.02,0:10:43.54,Default,,0,0,0,,你说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.42,0:10:45.88,Default,,0,0,0,,我是为了大家才战斗的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.51,0:10:48.14,Default,,0,0,0,,也是为了全人类在战斗呀
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.51,0:10:51.20,Default,,0,0,0,,知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.94,0:10:54.42,Default,,0,0,0,,我也不会再说琪珍的事 说好了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.48,0:10:56.20,Default,,0,0,0,,上吧 迪克
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.65,0:10:58.60,Default,,0,0,0,,好啊 这是男人之间的约定哟
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.60,0:11:07.54,Default,,0,0,0,,索安巴 变形为伊迪安德尔塔！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.71,0:11:08.28,Default,,0,0,0,,明白！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.28,0:11:15.31,Default,,0,0,0,,索瓦尼亚 变形为伊迪安诺瓦！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.71,0:11:20.82,Default,,0,0,0,,索空瓦 变形为伊迪安巴斯塔！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.31,0:11:35.22,Default,,0,0,0,,可恶的巨人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.60,0:11:39.25,Default,,0,0,0,,不要以为这伽尔波·吉克和之前的重机动机甲一样
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.94,0:11:43.05,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么办啊 迪克
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.00,0:11:45.05,Default,,0,0,0,,敌人就在近处吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.51,0:11:47.08,Default,,0,0,0,,他们在一点方向 还远着呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.68,0:11:50.34,Default,,0,0,0,,科斯摩 你在干什么 合体呀
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.91,0:11:51.57,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.11,0:11:55.25,Default,,0,0,0,,再往右边些 科斯摩！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.45,0:11:59.57,Default,,0,0,0,,可恶的巴夫·克兰！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.20,0:12:18.82,Default,,0,0,0,,科斯摩 你在干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.28,0:12:20.40,Default,,0,0,0,,我去发射加粒子炮
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.71,0:12:21.88,Default,,0,0,0,,交给你了 提克诺
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.08,0:12:23.40,Default,,0,0,0,,啊 他们追来了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.17,0:12:26.17,Default,,0,0,0,,科斯摩怎么了 敌人来了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.80,0:12:31.74,Default,,0,0,0,,迪克 快告诉我 敌人从哪里来？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.68,0:12:36.14,Default,,0,0,0,,正面 从稍稍下面点的地方过来了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.31,0:12:36.71,Default,,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.88,0:12:57.68,Default,,0,0,0,,加粒子炮！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.48,0:13:03.68,Default,,0,0,0,,在正面 它好大啊 科斯摩
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.80,0:13:05.48,Default,,0,0,0,,翻转！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.54,0:13:09.97,Default,,0,0,0,,打中了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.08,0:13:11.22,Default,,0,0,0,,应该打中了 但是...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.25,0:13:15.34,Default,,0,0,0,,好 它停下了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.22,0:13:18.51,Default,,0,0,0,,怎会这么轻易被你击败
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.37,0:13:21.57,Default,,0,0,0,,不错的团队协作
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.00,0:13:27.20,Default,,0,0,0,,后退 趁这个时机我们快合体
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.71,0:13:28.80,Default,,0,0,0,,迪克 要合体了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.22,0:13:31.17,Default,,0,0,0,,明白 合体的信号...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.85,0:13:33.31,Default,,0,0,0,,有了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.60,0:13:34.82,Default,,0,0,0,,好 合体！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.00,0:13:35.48,Default,,0,0,0,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.97,0:13:40.08,Default,,0,0,0,,变成巨人了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.60,0:13:41.74,Default,,0,0,0,,展开盖尔结界！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.88,0:13:44.14,Default,,0,0,0,,明白 伽尔波二号 三号机 快点
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.34,0:14:00.94,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么了 迪克
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.74,0:14:02.42,Default,,0,0,0,,敌人...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.60,0:14:09.82,Default,,0,0,0,,是对抗伊迪安专用的重机动机甲吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.60,0:14:13.77,Default,,0,0,0,,没有错 它不是为格斗战开发的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.68,0:14:16.97,Default,,0,0,0,,三台重机动机甲合成一台了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.08,0:14:19.91,Default,,0,0,0,,敌人到底有什么阴谋
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.22,0:14:23.08,Default,,0,0,0,,难不成是为对抗伊迪安的重机动机甲吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.82,0:14:25.68,Default,,0,0,0,,不会这么简单就开发出来的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.97,0:14:31.02,Default,,0,0,0,,重机动机甲合成一台了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.91,0:14:32.82,Default,,0,0,0,,到底有什么企图
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.37,0:14:48.74,Default,,0,0,0,,科斯摩 要分开了 拉开距离
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.88,0:14:49.85,Default,,0,0,0,,别让他们分开
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.31,0:14:53.60,Default,,0,0,0,,接近进入格斗战的话 就张开盖尔结界了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.42,0:14:56.77,Default,,0,0,0,,这样也不能进行掩护射击
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.28,0:14:59.00,Default,,0,0,0,,科斯摩那家伙 为什么要远离开
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.71,0:15:01.11,Default,,0,0,0,,哈达利 舰体左转
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.57,0:15:07.65,Default,,0,0,0,,看我打中你 混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.02,0:15:12.82,Default,,0,0,0,,想挡住吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.48,0:15:17.54,Default,,0,0,0,,可恶的巨人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.34,0:15:23.80,Default,,0,0,0,,伽尔波·吉克 陷入格斗战
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.80,0:15:28.80,Default,,0,0,0,,吉杰那家伙 想测试巨人的格斗性能吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.62,0:15:31.02,Default,,0,0,0,,不能让他一直继续下去
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.54,0:15:34.08,Default,,0,0,0,,伽尔波·吉克还有更多的力量没展现出来
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.94,0:15:36.68,Default,,0,0,0,,这样没事吗 达拉姆大人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.05,0:15:38.60,Default,,0,0,0,,只有那点程度就不算是新兵器了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.54,0:15:46.00,Default,,0,0,0,,破坏他们的思考回路 展开盖尔结界！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.20,0:15:46.54,Default,,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.20,0:15:48.00,Default,,0,0,0,,盖尔结界？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.20,0:15:48.74,Default,,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.42,0:15:52.08,Default,,0,0,0,,可理解为能破坏脑细胞的光束
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.60,0:15:54.60,Default,,0,0,0,,我们开发出了那种东西吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.91,0:15:59.25,Default,,0,0,0,,我们已找到证据 人的思考是伊迪的力量之源
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.68,0:16:03.54,Default,,0,0,0,,这样的话 就可以削弱巨人的战斗力
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.82,0:16:08.31,Default,,0,0,0,,就是说 直接破坏驾驶员的大脑 就可毫发无伤地得到巨人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.25,0:16:25.77,Default,,0,0,0,,啊 那是什么光
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.85,0:16:34.48,Default,,0,0,0,,头...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.22,0:16:39.11,Default,,0,0,0,,这是什么？ 为什么突然头好痛...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.37,0:16:43.77,Default,,0,0,0,,还要五分钟
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.08,0:16:48.48,Default,,0,0,0,,贝斯
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.82,0:16:50.17,Default,,0,0,0,,伊迪安的动作停止了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.54,0:16:51.85,Default,,0,0,0,,科斯摩 科斯摩
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.17,0:16:53.68,Default,,0,0,0,,快回答 怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.71,0:17:01.11,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么回事 伊迪安驾驶员的脑波紊乱了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.17,0:17:02.85,Default,,0,0,0,,脑波？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.11,0:17:03.68,Default,,0,0,0,,索罗船
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.17,0:17:06.25,Default,,0,0,0,,接近伊迪安 得去救他们
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.82,0:17:11.14,Default,,0,0,0,,不要让外星人的船接近巨人！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.51,0:17:23.91,Default,,0,0,0,,卡拉拉 你不知道吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.97,0:17:25.05,Default,,0,0,0,,那重机动机甲的事
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.37,0:17:26.00,Default,,0,0,0,,我不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.62,0:17:27.51,Default,,0,0,0,,那个光芒...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.02,0:17:29.34,Default,,0,0,0,,再离伊迪安近些！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.77,0:17:38.88,Default,,0,0,0,,巴夫·克兰已经了解了伊迪的事
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.34,0:17:39.97,Default,,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.34,0:17:43.08,Default,,0,0,0,,那个光芒是专门对付伊迪安的武器
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.97,0:17:46.77,Default,,0,0,0,,了解伊迪的秘密后研发出专门应对的兵器吗...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.20,0:17:50.08,Default,,0,0,0,,面对不断投入新武器的巴夫·克兰
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.62,0:17:52.08,Default,,0,0,0,,我们能赢得了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.62,0:17:54.48,Default,,0,0,0,,好 掩护伽尔波·吉克
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.62,0:18:12.17,Default,,0,0,0,,琪珍？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.08,0:18:16.60,Default,,0,0,0,,琪珍！琪珍！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.02,0:18:26.11,Default,,0,0,0,,迪克 迪克 没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.77,0:18:27.14,Default,,0,0,0,,迪克？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.31,0:18:32.51,Default,,0,0,0,,岂能被这样打败？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.91,0:18:34.14,Default,,0,0,0,,敌人在正面吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.60,0:18:35.80,Default,,0,0,0,,敌人在正面吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.17,0:18:40.80,Default,,0,0,0,,快帮我一把...迪克
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.11,0:18:42.02,Default,,0,0,0,,这家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.20,0:18:49.82,Default,,0,0,0,,迪克 敌人怎么样了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.31,0:18:52.94,Default,,0,0,0,,怪光线变弱了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.82,0:18:54.68,Default,,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.17,0:19:03.77,Default,,0,0,0,,躲开！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.57,0:19:12.11,Default,,0,0,0,,它又回到以前的状态了...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.11,0:19:16.20,Default,,0,0,0,,头痛感消失了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.62,0:19:17.02,Default,,0,0,0,,趁现在
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.45,0:19:18.40,Default,,0,0,0,,科斯摩 卡莎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.74,0:19:19.91,Default,,0,0,0,,快让伊迪安归舰！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.05,0:19:20.80,Default,,0,0,0,,要回去吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.28,0:19:22.02,Default,,0,0,0,,动作快点
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.37,0:19:23.08,Default,,0,0,0,,但是...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.40,0:19:24.42,Default,,0,0,0,,我要打垮他们！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.82,0:19:25.51,Default,,0,0,0,,科斯摩
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.57,0:19:38.25,Default,,0,0,0,,逃了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.77,0:19:43.00,Default,,0,0,0,,短距离DS航行！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.77,0:19:44.94,Default,,0,0,0,,短距离DS航行？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.48,0:19:48.37,Default,,0,0,0,,看了DS探测器 我们可以做小位置的DS航行
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.88,0:19:49.28,Default,,0,0,0,,知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.77,0:19:50.25,Default,,0,0,0,,乔立巴！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.54,0:19:51.60,Default,,0,0,0,,主引擎全开！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.05,0:19:52.57,Default,,0,0,0,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.94,0:19:59.74,Default,,0,0,0,,进入亚空间飞行了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.88,0:20:05.42,Default,,0,0,0,,发射生物发信器
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.05,0:20:19.14,Default,,0,0,0,,有这发射生物发信器
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.00,0:20:23.28,Default,,0,0,0,,你们即使跑到宇宙尽头 也照样找得着
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.68,0:20:24.77,Default,,0,0,0,,目标地球！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.97,0:20:25.80,Default,,0,0,0,,地球？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.20,0:20:27.60,Default,,0,0,0,,快设定坐标
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.97,0:20:29.25,Default,,0,0,0,,快 设定坐标为地球
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.45,0:20:30.02,Default,,0,0,0,,目标地球
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.60,0:20:33.14,Default,,0,0,0,,地球...地球
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.11,0:20:35.54,Default,,0,0,0,,坐标设定完毕
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.62,0:20:37.60,Default,,0,0,0,,X Y 各轴设定完毕
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.22,0:20:38.77,Default,,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.40,0:20:40.25,Default,,0,0,0,,DS航行停止
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.05,0:21:16.71,Default,,0,0,0,,地球...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.71,0:21:18.51,Default,,0,0,0,,我们回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.80,0:21:20.65,Default,,0,0,0,,那就是地球
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.05,0:21:22.71,Default,,0,0,0,,是地球
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.91,0:21:25.11,Default,,0,0,0,,我们的母星
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.62,0:21:30.40,Default,,0,0,0,,那就是...地球
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.08,0:21:31.77,Default,,0,0,0,,地球
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.57,0:21:33.85,Default,,0,0,0,,你们的母星
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.34,0:21:36.00,Default,,0,0,0,,也是你新的母星
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.05,0:21:40.28,Default,,0,0,0,,从今以后 如果你有一丝一毫想回巴夫·克兰的意思
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.71,0:21:43.22,Default,,0,0,0,,我就不得不把你处死
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.68,0:21:47.48,Default,,0,0,0,,贝斯 这和我的地球没有区别
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.40,0:21:50.88,Default,,0,0,0,,我是这么认为的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.20,0:21:57.85,Default,,0,0,0,,这样就...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.60,0:22:00.68,Default,,0,0,0,,终于撑过了无数战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.31,0:22:03.20,Default,,0,0,0,,是啊 我们...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.60,0:22:06.60,Default,,0,0,0,,终于到达了地球 索罗船也没被击毁
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.02,0:22:08.62,Default,,0,0,0,,那样不好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.25,0:22:09.68,Default,,0,0,0,,可是
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.54,0:22:12.22,Default,,0,0,0,,我还是没有为琪珍报仇
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.51,0:22:14.00,Default,,0,0,0,,科斯摩...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.88,0:22:17.25,Default,,0,0,0,,对...对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.45,0:22:25.37,Default,,0,0,0,,打开与参谋本部的通信回路
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.14,0:22:34.34,Default,,0,0,0,,科斯摩他们的母星 水之行星展现在眼前
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.37,0:22:38.48,Default,,0,0,0,,索罗船和地球的通讯也开始了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.11,0:22:40.48,Default,,0,0,0,,怀着心中的激动
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.85,0:22:52.60,Default,,0,0,0,,地球近在眼前 但索罗船被拒绝接纳
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.57,0:22:56.08,Default,,0,0,0,,和唯一理解索罗船苦衷的人 科尔波克一起
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.37,0:22:58.80,Default,,0,0,0,,谢莉鲁潜入了月面基地
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.57,0:23:02.77,Default,,0,0,0,,但是 科尔波克被地球人的子弹击倒了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.60,0:23:07.31,Default,,0,0,0,,一个人逃出的谢莉鲁 能带回伊迪的秘密吗
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.17,0:23:13.34,Default,,0,0,0,,下集 传说巨神伊迪安 月面基地紧急潜入
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.79,0:23:34.67,OP-ED,NTP,0,0,0,,被唯一一颗 属于我的星球所抛弃
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.96,0:23:42.01,OP-ED,NTP,0,0,0,,誓要能跟你一起 踏上无尽旅程
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.30,0:23:47.56,OP-ED,NTP,0,0,0,,无意间分享 我们的情感
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.52,0:23:54.94,OP-ED,NTP,0,0,0,,同甘共苦 寻欢作乐
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.28,0:24:01.03,OP-ED,NTP,0,0,0,,飞越无限宇宙
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.66,0:24:07.62,OP-ED,NTP,0,0,0,,我为你送上真挚的祈愿
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.95,0:24:13.58,OP-ED,NTP,0,0,0,,穿过无尽银河
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.29,0:24:20.97,OP-ED,NTP,0,0,0,,我为你带去真心的祝福
